p.cl:
With these witnesses: the lord Walter Oliphant, justice of Lothian; the lord
                  William, chancellor of the lord king; the lord John of
                  Maxwell, chamberlain of the lord king; the lord Robert of
                  Roos; the lord Ranulf of Bunckle; the lord Bernard Fraser;
                  the lord Thomas son of Ranulf; the lord Thomas de la Haye;
                  David, clerk of Walter Oliphant; and many others.
